{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"body":"Releasing back to open: this is a bot-authored binding-drift ALERT ticket whose closure is owned by the reconcile-bridge canary's close-on-recovery automation, not manual close. The code fix is merged (Gerrit 848) and the canary --class break is fixed (Gerrit 853). Binding drift has recovered (live bridge-fsck: 0 actionable drift). Returning to 'open' so the now-fixed canary auto-closes this alert on its next recovery pass (the correct lifecycle), rather than force-closing manually."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1784506578183449001,"uuid":"417789f9-e18a-40fd-b828-a9b7e28d8ee1"}